{"tid":2175176,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[宅奇恐怖台] 印尼恐怖驚Pamali : Indonesian Folklore Horror","createTime":"2020-08-26T10:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T11:28:26.000Z","uid":361375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7cddb35fd53c2c06a4b8e484f0db868c9d1a0421","tid":2175176,"uid":361375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"大家好啊喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日想介紹一隻2018年年尾出品既恐怖GAME比大家<br />\n呢隻GAME就係Pamali : Indonesian Folklore Horror (禁忌: 印尼民間恐怖傳說)<br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/854570/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1587920532\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F854570%2Fheader_tchinese.jpg%3Ft%3D1587920532&h=09709198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/854570/extras/steamPage_7A.jpg?t=1587920532\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F854570%2Fextras%2FsteamPage_7A.jpg%3Ft%3D1587920532&h=27269846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成隻GAME一共有4章(有3章係DLC)，每章都係講述唔同傳說鬼怪同傳統故事<br />\n玩家係每個故事入邊既互動，對物品既使用同決定，都會影響故事最後既結局。<br />\n記得當年試玩已經好深印象同好撚驚，不過正式出版後唔知係咪Home Sweet Home既原故，呢隻GAME好似冇得到好大回響(但即使係咁，STEAM依然係極度好評)<br />\n雖然已經係成年幾前既事，但最近決定挖返出黎同大家分享。<br />\n今晚<strong>9點半</strong>我會開台直播呢隻game，如果唔介意的話就陪下我啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/shimutsuki_aki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fshimutsuki_aki&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatg4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=f028d976\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/shimutsuki_aki</a>"},{"pid":"c90ea950064104197b6477af2d80b5caeb1ca2b7","tid":2175176,"uid":361375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"開台前推一野"},{"pid":"0bf01c53aea0485e44b9881920999e8408b12850","tid":2175176,"uid":361375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:29:09.